00:01:21.540 --> 00:01:27.650
Dirty Little Secrets is an art series by Sara
Rosado using dirt from local parks as a medium.

00:01:27.650 --> 00:01:33.720
Some of her dirty little secrets include Lonely
Panda, Ants, New York Skyline, and a Cat.

00:01:33.720 --> 00:01:38.229
Coiffure le Bird is a photo series by photographer
Rene Mesman.

00:01:38.229 --> 00:01:44.079
Using both a hairstylist and an art director
the series includes san owl, crow, and a falcon.

00:01:44.079 --> 00:01:48.689
And now for "The Pinks" a masculine figures
in pink series done by Scott Scheildy

00:01:48.689 --> 00:02:04.140
1,000 shadows is an ongoing street art series
by artist Herbert Baglione.

00:02:04.140 --> 00:02:09.200
In this set he used an abandoned psychiatric
hospital in Italy to showcase some of his

00:02:09.200 --> 00:02:11.019
haunting silhouette paintings.

